{"word":"H3975 - מְאוּרָה - mᵉʼûwrâh - meh-oo-raw' - Den","slug":"H3975","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מְאוּרָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mᵉʼûwrâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>meh-oo-raw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Den"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D0;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E8;&#x05D4; - m<sup>e</sup>'u&#x0302;ra&#x0302;h</b> - <i>meh-oo-raw'</i><p/>Feminine passive participle of <a href=\"#/H215\">H215</a>; something <i>lighted</i>, that is, an <i>aperture</i>; by implication a <i>crevice</i> or <i>hole</i> of a serpent: - den."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H215\">H215</a>, <a href=\"#/H216\">H216</a>, <a href=\"#/H217\">H217</a>, <a href=\"#/H218\">H218</a>, <a href=\"#/H219\">H219</a>, <a href=\"#/H221\">H221</a>, <a href=\"#/H222\">H222</a>, <a href=\"#/H223\">H223</a>, <a href=\"#/H224\">H224</a>, <a href=\"#/H2971\">H2971</a>, <a href=\"#/H2972\">H2972</a>, <a href=\"#/H3974\">H3974</a>"}]}